《'''高地戰'''》（{{kor|k=고지전|rm=Gojijeon|hanja=高地戰}}，{{lang-en|''The Front Line''}}），是一部於2011年上映以戰爭為題材的[[韓國電影|韓國電影]]，採取1953年《[[朝鮮停戰協議|朝鮮停戰協議]]》前的[[韓戰|韓戰]]為主題<ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|Lee, Maggie (9 August 2011). [http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/frontline-film-review-220991 "The Frontline: Film Review"]. ''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''. Retrieved 2011-10-14.}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Hyo-won|title='Front' brings harrowing views of war|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2012/06/141_90862.html|work=[[韓國時報|The Korea Times]]|date=11 July 2011|accessdate=2012-12-18|archive-date=2012-12-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DHFWVplY?url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2012/06/141_90862.html|dead-url=no}}}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web|last=Elley|first=Derek|title=The Front Line|url=http://www.filmbiz.asia/reviews/the-front-line|work={{Link-en|亞洲電影資訊|Film Business Asia|Film Business Asia}}|date=27 July 2011|accessdate=2012-12-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513063440/http://www.filmbiz.asia/reviews/the-front-line|archivedate=2012年5月13日}}}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web|last=Kuipers|first=Richard|title=The Front Line|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117946413/|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=23 October 2011|accessdate=2012-12-18|archive-date=2012-12-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DHFbRTml?url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117946413/|dead-url=no}}}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web|last=Paquet|first=Darcy|title=The Front Line|url=http://koreanfilm.org/kfilm11.html#frontline|work=Koreanfilm.org|accessdate=2012-06-29|archive-date=2011-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110504141548/http://koreanfilm.org/kfilm11.html#frontline|dead-url=yes}}}}</ref>，是導演[[張薰_(韓國導演)|張薰]]繼《{{Link-en|義兄弟 (電影)|Secret Reunion|義兄弟}}》和《{{Link-en|電影就是電影|Rough Cut (2008 film)}}》之後執導的第三部作品<ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite news|last=Park|first=Sung-hee|ti